metadata.name: Raregotchi Toy #1
metadata.description:
This is a sealed TOY. One of the original 3000 Raregotchi Toys. A truly rare and pristine collectible. But will it stay this way forever? Will you resist the urge to open it?

Opening a sealed TOY allows you to mint your OG PETS and create your Raregotchi Lineage by giving your PETS a unique FAMILY name.
